<%- include('../partials/head', { activeTab: 'help' }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-purple-900 to-slate-900 min-h-screen font-sans text-white">

  <%- include('../partials/nav') %>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 relative z-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-10">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-300">1. How do I book a home?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2">Browse available homes on the homepage, click "Details" on the one you like, then use the "Book Now" button to complete your reservation.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-300">2. How can I become a host?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2">Sign up as a host and use the "Add Home" option in your dashboard to list your property. Make sure to include clear photos and accurate details.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-300">3. Can I cancel my booking?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2">Yes, you can cancel your booking from the "My Bookings" section. Cancellation policies may vary depending on the host.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-300">4. What if I face issues during my stay?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2">If you encounter any problems, please contact our support team through the "Contact Us" page or email us directly. We're here to help!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Item -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-300">5. How do I reset my password?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-2">On the login page, click "Forgot Password" and follow the steps to reset your password via email.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
